{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"59f569cbef","title":"中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革关于纪念今年“五一”国际劳动节的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2a846198f8","index":0,"year":1968,"month":4,"day":24,"articleId":"59f569cbef","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"新闻广播和出版","id":"268718f23b","type":"主题"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"文化宗教和社会生活","id":"6d08cec53d","type":"主题"},{"name":"中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革联发","id":"cbee4acb80","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0dabd7ef8c","type":"title","text":"中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革关于纪念今年“五一”国际劳动节的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"59f569cbef","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eba0cfa468","type":"paragraph","text":"一、一九六八年的“五一”国际劳动节的庆祝活动，仍照过去规定，采取分散纪念的办法，不搞全市性的大型集体游行。各地可在市内工厂、学校、机关、部队、街道各单位分别举行小型的庆祝集会。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"59f569cbef","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1634d37141","type":"paragraph","text":"二、今年“五一”节，一概不邀请外宾参加活动。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"59f569cbef","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"37bc9ece71","type":"paragraph","text":"三、加强敌情观念，提高革命警惕性。国防前线要特别加强警戒，城市要加强治安管理工作厂矿、企业、机关、学校要加强内部的安全保卫，严防叛徒、特务、顽固不化的走资派和地、富、反、坏、右分子的破坏活动。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"59f569cbef","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"060a0f0ac7","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六八年四月二十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"59f569cbef","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"44888701c2","type":"paragraph","text":"附一九六八年纪念“五一”国际劳动节标语口号。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"59f569cbef","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ee111dde6","type":"paragraph","text"